No. 11-7034. James Niblock, Petitioner v. United States District Court for the Eastern District of Virginia, et al. 565 U.S. 1073, 132 S. Ct. 799,

181 L. Ed. 2d 509,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8340, November 28, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 453 Fed. Appx. 393.
